    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-01-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-01-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="294" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d294">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Blaine</persName> to Señor
                                    <persName type="to">Lazcano</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-01-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 20,
                                1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the
                            receipt of your note of the 16th instant, in which you state that on the
                            6th of the same month a naval division of the Republic of Chile revolted
                            in the harbor of Valparaiso; that your Government has outlawed the
                            revolting squadron and directs you to inform me that it is not
                            responsible for the acts of the rebels in respect to foreigners or
                            citizens.</p>
                <p>In making this acknowledgment, it is proper that this Government should
                            reserve the right to consider upon the facts and the law any case that
                            may arise involving the declaration which you communicate.</p>
                <p>Accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">James G. Blaine</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
